  <!-- EN: The child of an illicit affair, [PAWN_nameDef] was bought up by nuns in a medieval convent. [PAWN_pronoun] learned the value of hard work and submission, but was taught that technology is heretical. -->
  <ConventChild16.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]的出生是不被認同的，[PAWN_pronoun]被一所中世紀時代的修道院的修女扶養長大，學會了勤奮和奉獻的價值，但被教導科技是異端。</ConventChild16.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: convent child -->
  <ConventChild16.title>修道院兒童</ConventChild16.title>
  <!-- EN: illicit -->
  <ConventChild16.titleShort>私生子</ConventChild16.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] was a minor noble in an old kingdom on a medieval world. [PAWN_pronoun] grew up in a manor made of stone, served by bowing lowerclassmen.\n\nSuch a life teaches no technical skills and instils a lifelong aversion to manual labor - but [PAWN_nameDef] learned early the ways of social manipulation. -->
  <MedievalLordling19.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]是個出生在中世紀星球古老王國的年輕貴族。[PAWN_pronoun]在被石牆圍起、石磚搭建的莊園中成長，處處由恭順的下人服侍。\n\n這樣的生活使[PAWN_pronoun]沒有任何關於學術的知識，並且養成了排斥親手勞動的觀念────然而[PAWN_nameDef]卻早早掌握了馭人之術。</MedievalLordling19.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: medieval lordling -->
  <MedievalLordling19.title>中世紀領主</MedievalLordling19.title>
  <!-- EN: medieval lady -->
  <MedievalLordling19.titleFemale>中世紀女領主</MedievalLordling19.titleFemale>
  <!-- EN: lordling -->
  <MedievalLordling19.titleShort>領主</MedievalLordling19.titleShort>
  <!-- EN: lady -->
  <MedievalLordling19.titleShortFemale>女領主</MedievalLordling19.titleShortFemale>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] grew up pulling carts and digging holes on a medieval world. Simple manual labor is [PAWN_possessive] oldest companion - along with the master's lash.\n\n[PAWN_pronoun] didn't learn to read until age nine. -->
  <MedievalSlave49.baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef]出生在一個中世紀星球上，[PAWN_possessive]童年在每天不斷的推車、挖礦中度過。勞力工作是[PAWN_pronoun]最早的玩伴────主人的鞭子除外。\n\n[PAWN_pronoun]九歲之前都不識字。</MedievalSlave49.baseDesc>
  <!-- EN: medieval slave -->
  <MedievalSlave49.title>中世紀奴隸</MedievalSlave49.title>
  <!-- EN: slave -->
  <MedievalSlave49.titleShort>奴隸</MedievalSlave49.titleShort>
  
